  09 Jan 2015; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> -exult-1.2.ebuild,
  -files/exult-1.2-64bits.patch, -files/exult-1.2-gcc41.patch,
  -files/exult-1.2-gcc43.patch, -files/exult-1.2-gcc44.patch,
  -files/exult-1.2-libpng14.patch, -files/exult-1.2-libpng15.patch,
  -files/exult-1.2-x11link.patch:
  remove old and broken 'stable' version since it is not recommended for use by
  upstream

*exult-9999 (09 Jan 2015)

  09 Jan 2015; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> +exult-9999.ebuild:
  add live version of ebuild which is recommended for use by upstream.

  09 Jan 2015; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> -exult-1.4.9_rc1.ebuild,
  -files/exult-1.4.9_rc1-desktop.patch:
  clean known-broken version that upstream has removed

  15 May 2014; Ulrich Müller <ulm@gentoo.org> exult-1.2.ebuild,
  exult-1.4.9_rc1.ebuild:
  Fix USE dependency on media-libs/libsdl, "audio" USE flag was renamed to
  "sound", bug 357661.

  19 Oct 2011; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> exult-1.4.9_rc1.ebuild:
  autotools eclass isn't used

  15 Sep 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> exult-1.2.ebuild,
  +files/exult-1.2-libpng15.patch:
  Fix building with libpng15 wrt #380145 by Diego Elio Pettenò

